<section class='main__outer--page-view about__content-wrapper about__content-wrapper--intro'>
  <div class='main__inner--page-view'>
    <div class='logo'>Schoolbot</div>
    <div class='about__content about__content--intro'>
      <h1>Welcome!</h1>
      <p>SchoolBot is an application that maps the location of school busses. It is available to parents and school districts and works on a wide variety of devices.</p>
      <p>Read on to learn more about SchoolBot!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class='about__content-wrapper about__content-wrapper--district'>
  <div class='about__content about__content--district'>
    <h1>District</h1>
    <p class='about__content__copy--district'>If you work for a school district, you should know:</p>
    <ul class='about__content__list'>
      <li class='about__content__list-item--district'>SchoolBot uses your existing Zonar Ground Traffic Control subscription to provide live bus mapping.</li>
      <li class='about__content__list-item--district'>You can export student bus assignment data to SchoolBot from Versatrans or any other system.</li>
      <li class='about__content__list-item--district'>SchoolBot uses one-way encryption to ensure identifiable student data is never transmitted or stored.</li>
      <li class='about__content__list-item--district'>SchoolBot is fully <a class='about__content__link' href='http://www2.ed.gov/policy/gen/guid/fpco/ferpa/index.html' target='_blank'>FERPA-compliant.</a></li>
    </ul>
    <p>If you’d like to learn more about SchoolBot and find out how you can offer it in your district, enter your email address below and we’ll be in touch!</p>
    {{#if districtContactSubmitted}}
      <p>Thanks for your interest – we'll be in touch soon!</p>
    {{else}}
      <form {{action 'submitDistrictContact' on='submit'}}>
        {{input class='about__input about__input--district' placeholder='Enter your email address' value=districtContactEmail}}
        <button class='about__cta about__cta--district' type='submit' disabled={{districtContactInFlight}}>Submit</button>
      </form>
      {{#if districtContactErrored}}
        <p>There was a problem submitting your email. Check your network connection and try again, or <a href="mailto:schoolbot-contact@vermonster.com?subject=SchoolBot information request">email us directly</a>.</p>
      {{/if}}
    {{/if}}
  </div>
</section>

<section class='about__content-wrapper about__content-wrapper--parent'>
  <div class='about__content about__content--parent'>
    <h1>Parent</h1>
    <p class='about__content__copy--parent'>If you are a parent or a guardian of a student, you should know:</p>
    <ul class='about__content__list'>
      <li class='about__content__list-item--parent'>You can start and end your day feeling more relaxed because you know when your student’s bus is nearby.</li>
      <li class='about__content__list-item--parent'>The position of your student's bus is plotted on a map and is updated in real time. And if you have more than one student in the district, you can map buses for multiple students at once.</li>
      <li class='about__content__list-item--parent'>SchoolBot complies with federal regulations on storing student data, and connects to the Internet securely.</li>
    </ul>
    <p class='about__content__copy--parent'>If you think SchoolBot is a good idea, why not tell your school district administrators about it!</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class='about__content-wrapper about__content-wrapper--faq'>
  <div class='about__content'>
    <div class='about__content--faq__share'>
      <h1>Share</h1>
      <p>If SchoolBot seems interesting or useful, please spread the word on your networks!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

